Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.34,0:31:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们通过宇宙飞船研究彗星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've had great success studying comets
