Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.36,0:32:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于彗星到底是什么  它揭示了很多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it reveals much about what a comet really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.28,0:32:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(123,200)}{\an8}{\fn微软雅黑\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美国宇航局视频  {\fs16}深度空间1
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.23,0:32:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空间探测器已经告诉我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The space probes have told us
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.20,0:33:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星不是一个满是星尘的雪球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that a comet is more like a frozen watermelon
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.47,0:33:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更像一个冰冻西瓜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than it is a dirty snowball.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.29,0:33:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来它有一层的相当坚实的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There turns out to be a really hard compacted layer of ice
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.27,0:33:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混着尘埃的冰层\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with dust mixed in with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.00,0:33:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥泞的满是星尘的雪球状物位于内部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And then the slushy dirty snowball stuff is on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.48,0:33:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像个有层外皮  内部有瓤的西瓜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's kinda got a rind and then the watermelony stuff on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.72,0:33:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当它沿着轨道越来越靠近太阳  开始升温\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And as it gets closer to the sun on its orbit, it heats up,
