Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.49,0:33:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和彗星的间歇喷泉\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the geysers squirting out of the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.92,0:33:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn微软雅黑\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}样本1  深度撞击  坑位
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.78,0:33:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深度撞击探测器送回了令人炫目的图像\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Deep Impact probe returns stunning images,
