Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集相关物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to collect that material
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.74,0:33:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是从彗星表面挣脱的气体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's being degassed off the surface of a comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.22,0:33:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了捕获这些宝贵的粒子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To capture the precious particles,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.33,0:33:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星尘号部署了一个收集器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Stardust deploys a collector
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.94,0:34:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟网球拍的尺寸和形状差不多\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}about the size and shape of a tennis racquet.
