Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.51,0:34:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在捕获的几乎是最原始的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We're getting nearly the pristine material,
