Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.89,0:34:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本成分\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is composed and was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.89,0:34:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采集好物质后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once the material is gathered,
