Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.16,0:35:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必需氨基酸  维持生命的必需的基本物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to make proteins, a fundamental requirement for sustaining life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.94,0:35:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人推测说\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And there are some folks who suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.92,0:35:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彗星上也许有生物学有机体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that perhaps there could be biological organisms
