Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.85,0:35:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至会有类似流感病毒之类的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even, like, flu viruses or something could be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.33,0:35:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星尘号没有捕获到任何病毒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Stardust didn't capture any viruses,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.69,0:35:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是它的发现支持了那种理论\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But its discoveries support the theory
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.74,0:35:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为构成人类的生命基本物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that the very building blocks of the human race
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.72,0:35:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能形成于太空  并且在很久以前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}could have formed in space and they were long ago
